{
  "texts": [
    "As a result, a questionnaire was self-designed with partial adoption of modified items from certain existing studies (Getie, (2020); Orfan, (2020).",
    "The first part of the questionnaire deals with items related to the demographic profile of the participants.",
    "Of the next 12 items, four items each assesses cognitive, behavioral, and emotional perspectives.",
    "The last 20 items seek to collect data regarding the socio-cultural and educational factors affecting the attitudes of the respondents positively or negatively.",
    "The respondents were asked to mark their opinion on a 5-point Likert scale (5 = strongly agree, 4 = agree, 3 = neutral, 2 = disagree, and 1 = strongly disagree)."
  ]
}